(43, 'Undergraduate Programmes', 'Undergraduate Programmes', '<p>Undergraduate Programs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College offers the following three-year undergraduate programs leading to degrees:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science (BScGen)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science with Education (BScEd)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Chemistry (BScChem)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Petroleum Chemistry (BScPChem)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Molecular Biology and Biotechnology (BScMolBioBTech)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Applied Zoology (BScAppZoo)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Wildlife Science and Conservation(BScWSc)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Botanical Science (BScBotSc)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Microbiology (BScMicr)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Actuarial Sciences (BScActSc)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Meteorology (BScMet)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College also offers the following four-year undergraduate programs leading to degrees:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Geology (BScGeo)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Engineering Geology (BScEngGeo)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science with Geology (BSc-Geo)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Petroleum Geology (BScPGeo)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Undergraduate Programs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College offers the following three-year undergraduate programs leading to degrees:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science (BScGen)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science with Education (BScEd)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Chemistry (BScChem)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Petroleum Chemistry (BScPChem)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Molecular Biology and Biotechnology (BScMolBioBTech)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Applied Zoology (BScAppZoo)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Wildlife Science and Conservation(BScWSc)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Botanical Science (BScBotSc)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Microbiology (BScMicr)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Actuarial Sciences (BScActSc)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Meteorology (BScMet)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College also offers the following four-year undergraduate programs leading to degrees:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Geology (BScGeo)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Engineering Geology (BScEngGeo)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science with Geology (BSc-Geo)</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor of Science in Petroleum Geology (BScPGeo)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 'colleges/conas/programmes/undergraduate/undergraduate-programmes', '2017-10-26 05:44:25', 1, 10, 'colleges/conas/programmes/undergraduate/'),
(44, 'Postgraduate Programmes', 'Postgraduate Programmes', '<p><strong>Postgraduate Programs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College of Natural and Applied Sciences offers the following Masters programs:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Applied Botany</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Applied Sciences of Materials</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of&nbsp;Science in Applied Zoology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Biochemistry</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in&nbsp;Biodiversity and Conservation</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Chemistry</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Geology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Mathematical Modeling</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Mathematics</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Petroleum Geology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Physics</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science with Education</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Masters of&nbsp;Science in Wildlife Ecology&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Applied Microbiology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in &nbsp;Microbiology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Molecular Biology and Biotechnology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Integrated Environmental Management (MIEM) offered jointly with CoET.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from these Masters programs, the college also offers the following taught PhD programs:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PhD in Environmental Science</li>\r\n	<li>PhD in Molecular Biosciences and</li>\r\n	<li>PhD in Mathematics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Postgraduate Programs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College of Natural and Applied Sciences offers the following Masters programs:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Applied Botany</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Applied Sciences of Materials</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of&nbsp;Science in Applied Zoology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Biochemistry</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in&nbsp;Biodiversity and Conservation</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Chemistry</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Geology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Mathematical Modeling</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Mathematics</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Petroleum Geology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Physics</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science with Education</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Masters of&nbsp;Science in Wildlife Ecology&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Applied Microbiology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in &nbsp;Microbiology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Molecular Biology and Biotechnology</li>\r\n	<li>Masters of Science in Integrated Environmental Management (MIEM) offered jointly with CoET.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from these Masters programs, the college also offers the following taught PhD programs:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PhD in Environmental Science</li>\r\n	<li>PhD in Molecular Biosciences and</li>\r\n	<li>PhD in Mathematics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 'colleges/conas/programmes/postgraduate/postgraduate-programmes', '2017-10-26 05:47:48', 1, 10, 'colleges/conas/programmes/postgraduate/'),
