(47, 20, 1, 'about_us', 'About Us', 'About Us', 'TATAKI inaidara mbili ambazo ni idara ya lugha ya Kiswahili na isimu na idara ya fasihi, mawasiliano na uchapaji. Idara hizi kwa pamoja zinashirikiana katika ufundishaji wa programu mbalimbali. Pamoja na kujishughulisha na ufundishaji, utafiti na utoaji ushauri, hujishughulisha pia na shughuli za uchapaji na uchapishaji. Uchapishaji hulenga kazi zilizoandikwa kwa lugha ya Kiswahili na uchapaji hufanywa kwa kazi zote bila kujali zimeandikwa kwa lugha gani. Aidha, TATAKI hutoa huduma ya ushauri wa kitaalamu kwa watu mbalimbali.', 'TATAKI inaidara mbili ambazo ni idara ya lugha ya Kiswahili na isimu na idara ya fasihi, mawasiliano na uchapaji. Idara hizi kwa pamoja zinashirikiana katika ufundishaji wa programu mbalimbali. Pamoja na kujishughulisha na ufundishaji, utafiti na utoaji ushauri, hujishughulisha pia na shughuli za uchapaji na uchapishaji. Uchapishaji hulenga kazi zilizoandikwa kwa lugha ya Kiswahili na uchapaji hufanywa kwa kazi zote bila kujali zimeandikwa kwa lugha gani. Aidha, TATAKI hutoa huduma ya ushauri wa kitaalamu kwa watu mbalimbali.\r\n', NULL, 'fa-flag-o', '', 'institutes/iks/institutes/iks/institute-of-kiswahili-studies-(iks)', 'CT_FBC1', '0', 1, 1),
(50, 5, 1, 'SLIDESIDE', 'Achievements', 'Mafanikio', 'The College has been able to establish two (2) new Bachelor of Science Degree Programmes   * Number of practical training (PT) places secured in academic year 2012/13 increased by 11% *Number of consultancy reports and conference papers published by CoET staff members in academic year 2012/13 increased by 82% and 37% respectively *	Internally generated funds increased by 6%', 'The College has been able to establish two (2) new Bachelor of Science Degree Programmes   * Number of practical training (PT) places secured in academic year 2012/13 increased by 11% *Number of consultancy reports and conference papers published by CoET staff members in academic year 2012/13 increased by 82% and 37% respectively *	Internally generated funds increased by 6%', NULL, '', '', '', 'CT_HSR', '', 1, 1),
(51, 2, 2, 'Accommodation', 'Accomodation Services', 'Accomodation Services', 'The University Students Accommodation Bureau (USAB), a \r\nsemi independent unit, operates under the Dean of Students Office. USAB oversees the effective management of student accommodation facilities, including students halls of residence and hostels, ensuring that they are of acceptable standards. \r\n\r\nThere are important rules and regulations that have to be observed to ensure the effectiveness and efficiency \r\nof the USAB. These are stipulated in the Student By-Laws, \r\nAccommodation Policy and in the Accommodation Agreement Forms, and any other rules and regulations as shall be approved by the Chief Administrative Officer or the officer in charge at the material time.\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'The University Students Accommodation Bureau (USAB), a \r\nsemi independent unit, operates under the Dean of Students Office. USAB oversees the effective management of student accommodation facilities, including students halls of residence and hostels, ensuring that they are of acceptable standards. \r\n\r\nThere are important rules and regulations that have to be observed to ensure the effectiveness and efficiency \r\nof the USAB. These are stipulated in the Student By-Laws, \r\nAccommodation Policy and in the Accommodation Agreement Forms, and any other rules and regulations as shall be approved by the Chief Administrative Officer or the officer in charge at the material time.\r\n', NULL, 'fa-bed', '', '/campus-life/accomodation', 'MT_CTL', 'http://www2.udsm.ac.tz/web/index.php/campus-life/accomodation', 1, 1),
